Path 1: /home/rinaldo/arquivo1.txt
Path 2: /home/rinaldo/arquivos
Path 1 exist? true
Path 2 exist? false
Path 1 does NOT exist? false
Path 2 does NOT exist? true
Is Path 1 a directory? false
Is Path 1 a common file? true
Is Path 1 a symbolic link? false
